# API Conventions

## Client-Side

All REST calls live in `client/src/api/`. Never make fetch/axios calls directly inside components or hooks â€” import from the api module.

```js
// âťŚ BAD â€” fetch inside a component
const res = await fetch('/api/surgeries');

// âś… GOOD â€” import from api module
import { getSurgeries } from '../api/surgeries';
const surgeries = await getSurgeries();
```

No Parse SDK on the client â€” ever.

## Endpoint Reference

| Method | Path | Role | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | any | Returns JWT |
| POST | `/api/auth/signup` | public | Creates User (accountOwner) + Account |
| POST | `/api/auth/reset-password` | any | Initiates password reset |
| GET | `/api/surgeries` | owner / doctor / tech | List account surgeries (technicians: all in account) |
| POST | `/api/surgeries` | owner / doctor | Create surgery |
| GET | `/api/surgeries/:id` | owner/user | Surgery detail |
| PATCH | `/api/surgeries/:id` | owner/user | Update surgery (goal, status, etc.) |
| POST | `/api/surgeries/:id/extraction` | user | Update extraction entry counts |
| POST | `/api/surgeries/:id/placement` | user | Update placement count |
| GET | `/api/users` | owner / doctor | List team in account |
| POST | `/api/users` | owner / doctor | Create technician or doctor |
| DELETE | `/api/users/:id` | owner / doctor | Remove user (cannot remove clinic owner unless owner) |
| GET | `/api/settings` | owner | Get account branding + owner profile |
| PATCH | `/api/settings` | owner | Update account branding + owner profile |
| GET | `/api/settings/options` | owner | Get account dropdown option lists |
| PATCH | `/api/settings/options` | owner | Update a specific option list |
| GET | `/api/patients` | owner | List patients in account |
| GET | `/api/patients/:id` | owner | Patient detail + surgery history |
| POST | `/api/patients` | owner / doctor | Create patient |
| PATCH | `/api/patients/:id` | owner / doctor | Update patient |
| DELETE | `/api/patients/:id` | owner / doctor | Delete patient |
| GET | `/api/accounts` | admin | List all accounts |
| POST | `/api/accounts` | admin | Create account |
| PATCH | `/api/accounts/:id` | admin | Edit account |
| DELETE | `/api/accounts/:id` | admin | Delete account |
| GET | `/api/defaults` | admin | Get global default option lists |
| PATCH | `/api/defaults` | admin | Update global default option lists |

## Server-Side

- Auth middleware (`middleware/auth.js`) validates JWT on every protected route
- Role guard (`middleware/roles.js`) checks `req.user.roles.includes(role)` â€” uses array, never string equality; clinic staff mutations use `requireOwnerOrDoctor` (account owner or doctor)
- All non-admin queries are scoped by `accountId` from the JWT payload
